title: Kiss - Anaheim,CA 1976-08-20 NEW Mint version
description:
Description:

Here is the soundboard source off the now classic Anaheim show released on the Zodiac lable in Japan recently.
I haven't seen it before on the tracker and as i just got in my silver disc i decided to rip it in case some of you might need it.
A very cool altarnate version of this classic show now finally from the soundboard and according to the bootleggers sourced from the master cassette.
Btw if anyone has the Waterbury gig also released via Japanese bootleggers recently it would be great to see it uploaded here at some point.
